sources.description:
They Stamped an Outlaw's Name on every Bullet! 
Shamrock Ellison becomes Marshal, aided by Lucky Hayden, they set out to capture the notorious outlaw gang led by the elusive Cat, seeking vengeance for his parents' murder.

Original title: Fast on the Draw (1950)

Colorized version: https://youtu.be/8ArzTT7jsLs

Director: Thomas Carr
Writers: Ron Ormond, Maurice Tombragel, Richard Martinsen
Stars: James 'Shamrock' Ellison, Russell 'Lucky' Hayden, Raymond Hatton
Genre: Classics, Western
